title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Suicide won't oure shyness problems.” [Headline over Beth Winship's teen-advice column, Morning Union, Springfield, (Massachusetts), 9 January 1987. Submitted by Mrs. John E. Mann, Longmeadow, Massachusetts.]
